text: Božo Jemc (born 10 March 1940) is a Slovenian ski jumper. He competed in the normal hill and large hill events at the 1964 Winter Olympics. ==References== Category:1940 births Category:Living people Category:Slovenian male ski jumpers Category:Olympic ski jumpers of Yugoslavia Category:Ski jumpers at the 1964 Winter Olympics Category:People from Bled
